      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Koei Tecmo Games [3,119 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games">Koei Tecmo</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Team NINJA [664 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/koei-tecmo-games/team-ninja">Team NINJA</a> have released a 17-minute gameplay showcase video for dark samurai <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,939 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a> sequel <em><a title="Games > Nioh 3 [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/nioh-3">Nioh 3</a></em>. <span id="more-1020998"></span></p><p>The video description reads, “Dive into the world of <em>Nioh 3</em> with this gameplay showcase demonstrating unique yokai, historical heroes, samurai and ninja-style combat, and the Crucible. ”</p><p><em>Nioh 3</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,250 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,331 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3681010/Nioh_3/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on February 6. A demo is due out on January 29, and save data can be carried over to the full game.</p><p>Watch the footage below.</p><h2><span>Gameplay Showcase</span></h2><p><iframe title="Nioh 3 – Gameplay Showcase" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zZhatyRPtdk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
